ont velocity in the model due to the lack of\nresolution at the fronts, even though the energy loss is not likely to account\nfor the large gap on the strength of the fronts between the model result and\nthe semi-geostrophic limit solution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Nov 2016 16:47:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 Apr 2017 21:23:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-27"}
