ieve a visual quality that is\ncompetitive with the state-of-the-art while maintaining interactive speeds and\nproviding the user with an intuitive interface to tweak the results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Nov 2016 15:30:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 21 Nov 2016 18:26:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 31 Jul 2017 19:40:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-02"}
