 wire systems for both DC and AC biases, and\nfind a novel signature of the traversal time for electrons crossing the wire in\nthe time-dependent cross-lead current correlations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Nov 2016 15:57:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-03"}
